column5: After 24 hours of no sleep, I went out for walleye opener.  Did well. Lotsa walleye in the 14-16" range, a few hammer handles, two pike around 27" and a buncha small bass.  Not alot of pics, im tired. Goodnight
Nice collection of fish you got up there.
Thanks guys!  Gotta second wind and a fishing addiction. Few hours sleep and im ready to head back.  Im looking for 2 nice pike, 25-28" and ill be happy
Mission accomplished! Time to eat and start over tomorrow?
